OL,3,CTrump names new Homeland Security
OL,4,CSecretary, replacing Kristi Noem
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has said he
OL,7,Fis replacing his Homeland Security
OL,8,FSecretary Kristi Noem.
OL,10,FNoem has faced controversy in recent
OL,11,Fmonths over her department's
OL,12,Fimmigration enforcement tactics in
OL,13,FMinnesota, during which two US
OL,14,Fcitizens were killed.
OL,16,FShe will be replaced with Oklahoma
OL,17,FRepublican Senator Markwayne Mullin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
