OL,3,CTrump names new Homeland Security
OL,4,CSecretary, replacing Kristi Noem
OL,6,FTrump made the announcement on social
OL,7,Fmedia on Thursday, two days after Noem
OL,8,Ffaced a grilling on Capitol Hill from
OL,9,FGOP members as well as Democrats.
OL,11,FTrump says he'll make Noem a "Special
OL,12,FEnvoy for The Shield of the Americas,"
OL,13,Fa new security initiative that he said
OL,14,Fwould focus on the Western Hemisphere.
OL,16,FWriting on social media platform,
OL,17,FTruth Social, Trump said Noem had had
OL,18,F"numerous and spectacular results."
OL,26,@tD@fO]
