OL,3,CTrump names new Homeland Security
OL,4,CSecretary, replacing Kristi Noem
OL,6,F"I am pleased to announce that the
OL,7,FHighly Respected United States Senator
OL,8,Ffrom the Great State of Oklahoma,
OL,9,FMarkwayne Mullin, will become the
OL,10,FUnited States Secretary of Homeland
OL,11,FSecurity (DHS), effective March 31,
OL,12,F2026," he wrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
