OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772758999
OL,3,CTrump names new Homeland Security
OL,4,CSecretary, replacing Kristi Noem
OL,6,F"The current Secretary, Kristi Noem,
OL,7,Fwho has served us well, and has had
OL,8,Fnumerous and spectacular results
OL,9,F(especially on the Border!), will be
OL,10,Fmoving to be Special Envoy for The
OL,11,FShield of the Americas, our new
OL,12,FSecurity Initiative in the Western
OL,13,FHemisphere we are announcing on
OL,14,FSaturday in Doral, Florida.
OL,16,F"I thank Kristi for her service at
OL,17,F"Homeland."
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@KO]
