OL,3,CTrump names new Homeland Security
OL,4,CSecretary, replacing Kristi Noem
OL,6,F"Serving 10 years in the United States
OL,7,FHouse of Representatives, and 3 in the
OL,8,FSenate, Markwayne has done a
OL,9,Ftremendous job representing the
OL,10,Fwonderful People of Oklahoma, where I
OL,11,Fwon all 77 out of 77 Counties ` in
OL,12,F2016, 2020, and 2024!
OL,14,F"A MAGA Warrior, and former undefeated
OL,15,Fprofessional MMA fighter, Markwayne
OL,16,Ftruly gets along well with people, and
OL,17,Fknows the Wisdom and Courage required
OL,18,Fto Advance our America First Agenda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
