OL,3,CTrump names new Homeland Security
OL,4,CSecretary, replacing Kristi Noem
OL,6,F"As the only Native American in the
OL,7,FSenate, Markwayne is a fantastic
OL,8,Fadvocate for our incredible Tribal
OL,9,FCommunities. Markwayne will work
OL,10,Ftirelessly to Keep our Border Secure,
OL,11,FStop Migrant Crime, Murderers, and
OL,12,Fother Criminals from illegally
OL,13,Fentering our Country, End the Scourge
OL,14,Fof Illegal Drugs and, MAKE AMERICA
OL,15,FSAFE AGAIN. Markwayne will make a
OL,16,Fspectacular Secretary of Homeland
OL,17,FSecurity. Thank you for your attention
OL,18,Fto this matter!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
